The paper discusses the impact of user pairing on the performance of two NOMA systems, which are related to information theory (cs.IT), networking (cs.NI), and system design (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions the concept of cognitive radio networks (cs.CR) and the potential application of NOMA in multimedia communication (cs.MM).
